	(text "Ven = 8V\nVen = Vin * Rbot/(Rtop+Rbottom)\nRatio of Rbottom/(Rtop+Rbottom)=1.08/8≈0.135\n\nStandardized Passives:\nratio = 45.3k / (300k + 45.3k) = 45.3k / 300k ≈ 0.131\n\nVin,on = 1.08 / 0.131 ≈ 8.24V\n\nVin,off = 0.92/0.131 = 7V\n\nR4 as a DNP 0 ohm resistor to force \nboost off in some cases"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
